Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.00,0:54:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.95,0:54:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So we seek out the people, you know, who have beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.95,0:54:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
