Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.15,0:56:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,people who drive and die from drugs and alcohol wouldn't be dying because they all feel guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.15,0:56:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.15,0:56:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconscious guilt is what leads the person to go off the bottom of the box in the first
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.15,0:56:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,place.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.15,0:56:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So feeling guilty about drugs and alcohol isn't going to be the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.15,0:56:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The unconscious guilt is what leads to the path of suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.15,0:56:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see all these people like you rolling the tire over a few times.
